{"tid":683584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮發布聲明　將對價值500億美元中國商品加徵關稅　最終清單於6月15日宣布","createTime":"2018-05-29T22:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T08:17:06.000Z","uid":147314,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0a75716e90bff022a4e1bf513961ec4aacc046fa","tid":683584,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:25:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/white-house-2018-5-29/4414837.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fwhite-house-2018-5-29%2F4414837.html&d=ssuBoWojxZlVBMezr6zkighMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=7f53ee62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/white-house-2018-5-29/4414837.html</a><br />\n<br />\n白宮發布聲明　將對價值500億美元中國商品加徵關稅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/BA94C9ED-8D86-4B48-A953-CE89EB0CA661_w1023_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2FBA94C9ED-8D86-4B48-A953-CE89EB0CA661_w1023_r1_s.jpg&h=1b82d62f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">美國財政部長努欽5月3號在北京參加貿易會談 (資料照片)</span><br />\n<br />\n美國白宮29日發布聲明，宣布將採取多種措施保護本國技術與知識產權免遭中國&ldquo;歧視性的、繁重的&rdquo;貿易行為的影響。<br />\n<br />\n這些措施包括：美國將對與獲取重要技術有關的中國個人和實體實施具體的投資限制並提升出口管制；美國將繼續針對中國在授予知識產權許可方面歧視性的行為違反相關協議尋求在世界貿易組織提起訴訟；根據《1974年貿易法》第301條款，美國將對價值500億美元、進口自中國的含有產業重要技術的商品徵收百分之25的關稅，最終的徵稅清單將於6月15日宣布，隨後不久將開始對有關產品徵稅。"},{"pid":"affecc298467b909ab9ad78cb2a0bb92da074302","tid":683584,"uid":147314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:26:49.000Z","msg":"在白宮發出聲明後，中國商務部迅速做出回應稱，對白宮的這項聲明&ldquo;既感到出乎意料，但也在意料之中&rdquo;。商務部的聲明說，白宮的這一做法&ldquo;顯然有悖於不久前中美雙方在華盛頓達成的共識。&rdquo;這份聲明還強調，&ldquo;無論美方出台什麼舉措，中方都有信心、有能力、有經驗捍衛中國人民利益和國家核心利益。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n白宮發布這一聲明正值美中兩國貿易爭端似乎有趨緩跡象之時。美國財政部長努欽不久前宣布美中之間的貿易戰暫時擱置，美國商務部長羅斯預計將於週六抵達北京，就緩解美中兩國間的貿易緊張繼續與中方進行磋商。<br />\n<br />\n美中雙方在5月19日舉行的最近一輪的貿易談判中達成協議，北京同意購買更多的美國商品以便&ldquo;大幅減少&rdquo;高額貿易逆差。但兩國達成一致的聲明中沒有提及任何具體的進口和出口目標。<br />\n<br />\n在美中雙方於華盛頓舉行磋商之後，美國財長努欽宣布世界最大的兩國經濟體已經達成共識，暫不對彼此施加高額新關稅。<br />\n<br />\n川普起初對達成協議表示讚揚，但隨後表示他對這一結果既不高興也不滿意。"},{"pid":"8ec0996e3b2852487ad942b1dd701390b846dc81","tid":683584,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:27:17.000Z","msg":"此外，美中兩國代表週一在世貿組織就美國總統川普指稱中國盜取美國創新思想進行爭論。美國駐世貿組織代表丹尼斯&bull;謝伊大使說，對於那些想要進入中國市場的公司，特別是那些與國有或國家領導的中國企業合作的公司來說，&ldquo;強迫性的技術轉讓&rdquo;通常都是一個不成文的規定。據路透社報道，謝伊在發言中說：&ldquo;這不是法治。實際上，正是中國的法律本身允許了這種脅迫。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n中國斷然否認了這一批評。中國常駐世界貿易組織代表張向晨大使在世貿組織會議上表示，中國沒有強迫性的技術轉讓。張向晨說美方的觀點涉及&ldquo;有罪推定&rdquo;。他說：&ldquo;事實是，這些監管舉措都沒有要求外國公司進行技術轉讓。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n白宮週二的聲明說，美國將繼續保護本國技術與知識產權，阻止非經貿方面的重要技術和知識產權向中國轉讓，並且提升中國市場准入。此外，美國還將呼籲中國移除其諸多的貿易壁壘，並且呼籲兩國間的關稅和其它稅負在實質和價值上能夠互惠互利。"},{"pid":"c9998d558413a5b0215762574081d690cfd56b2b","tid":683584,"uid":185197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:27:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35580dc9a4612c3906f74b990f98cfbcbd3c2ceb","tid":683584,"uid":8867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:32:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b9105723d0b54761bba664bb49c7296b4454bd4","tid":683584,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:32:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/president-donald-j-trump-confronting-chinas-unfair-trade-policies/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefings-statements%2Fpresident-donald-j-trump-confronting-chinas-unfair-trade-policies%2F&d=ssuBoWojxZlVBMezr6zkighMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=91f20525\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefings-statements/president-donald-j-trump-confronting-chinas-unfair-trade-policies/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>President Donald J. Trump is Confronting China&rsquo;s Unfair Trade Policies</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Issued on: May 29, 2018</span><br />\n<br />\n&quot;From now on, we expect trading relationships to be fair and to be reciprocal.&quot;<br />\n<em>President Donald J. Trump</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong>YEARS OF UNFAIR TRADE PRACTICES: China has consistently taken advantage of the American economy with practices that undermine fair and reciprocal trade.</strong><br />\n<br />\nFor many years, China has pursued industrial policies and unfair trade practices&mdash;including dumping, discriminatory non-tariff barriers, forced technology transfer, over capacity, and industrial subsidies&mdash;that champion Chinese firms and make it impossible for many United States firms to compete on a level playing field."},{"pid":"02a8640f6fa81b77b7316f56b6c55066e98f4576","tid":683584,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:35:26.000Z","msg":"China&rsquo;s industrial policies, such as its &ldquo;Made in China 2025&rdquo; plan, harm companies in the United States and around the world.<br />\n<br />\nChina imposes much higher tariffs on United States exports than the United States imposes on China.<br />\n<br />\n　China&rsquo;s average tariff rate is nearly three times higher than the average United States rate.<br />\n<br />\n　Certain products are even more imbalanced, for instance the United States charges a 2.5 percent tariff on Chinese cars, while China currently maintains a 25 percent tariff on cars from the United States."},{"pid":"462f6b71b40143abc6e5dbc4dfe1e7f3f2eb3be0","tid":683584,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:35:44.000Z","msg":"China has banned imports of United States agricultural products such as poultry, cutting off America&rsquo;s ranchers and farmers from a major market for their goods.<br />\n<br />\nChina has dumped and unfairly subsidized a range of goods for the United States market, undermining America&rsquo;s domestic industry.<br />\n<br />\n　In 2018 alone, the Trump Administration has found dumping or unfair subsidies on 13 different products, including steel wheels, cold-drawn mechanical tubing, tool chests and cabinets, forged steel fittings, aluminum foil, rubber bands, cast iron soil pipe and fittings, and large diameter welded pipe."},{"pid":"443072681dbd94568027a99fd4bbfe4fd2083929","tid":683584,"uid":147314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:35:54.000Z","msg":"In January 2018, the Trump Administration found that China&rsquo;s overproduction of steel and aluminum, and the resulting impact on global markets, is a circumstance that threatens to impair America&rsquo;s national security.<br />\n<br />\nThe United States has run a trade in goods deficit with China for years, including a $375 billion deficit in 2017 alone."},{"pid":"fd23a681a1ff6cee1c9c242989ce4ab6027aff54","tid":683584,"uid":147314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:38:21.000Z","msg":"太長，跳到尾段：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>PROTECTING AMERICAN INNOVATION AND CREATIVITY: President Trump has worked to defend America&rsquo;s intellectual property and proprietary technology from theft and other threats.</strong><br />\n<br />\nIn August 2017, the Administration initiated a Section 301 investigation into China&rsquo;s practices related to forced technology transfer, unfair licensing, and intellectual property policies.<br />\n<br />\nAfter USTR completed its Section 301 report in March 2018, the President directed the agencies to explore numerous actions to protect domestic technology and intellectual property.<br />\n<br />\nUnder President Trump&rsquo;s leadership:<br />\n<br />\n　The United States will impose a 25 percent tariff on $50 billion of goods imported from China containing industrially significant technology, including those related to the &ldquo;Made in China 2025&rdquo; program.  The final list of covered imports will be announced by June 15, 2018.<br />\n<br />\n　USTR will continue WTO dispute settlement against China originally initiated in March to address China&rsquo;s discriminatory technology licensing requirements.<br />\n<br />\n　The United States will implement specific investment restrictions and enhanced export controls for Chinese persons and entities related to the acquisition of industrially significant technology. The list of restrictions and controls will be announced by June 30, 2018."},{"pid":"f09591c2377ffff703e90a3f16145b750d20cb82","tid":683584,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T22:50:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ae7a09b8d205e632ab3241ead0eda1377e9858","tid":683584,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:29:02.000Z","msg":"500億太少"},{"pid":"7d9f7fd535eef5ca4b4016a7d24f4e39694120cc","tid":683584,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0ae7a09b8d205e632ab3241ead0eda1377e9858","tid":683584,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:29:02.000Z","msg":"500億太少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:35:32.000Z","msg":"逐步黎，呢單係3月22號第一單嗰單"},{"pid":"501a8c72d9027e3aafed9637a539b6179d6ed74c","tid":683584,"uid":33907,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:39:29.000Z","msg":"張向晨說美方的觀點涉及&ldquo;有罪推定&rdquo;<br />\n支那好似都係用有罪推定架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65033fde56ff0a01653059b18f6943aa326e27f1","tid":683584,"uid":64953,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:48:01.000Z","msg":"你又估到 又估唔到 咁你即係估唔估到"},{"pid":"2c623498c7cac6ee620d358b34f00ea998a9c56c","tid":683584,"uid":78016,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T23:48:49.000Z","msg":"班左膠同反侵撚出黎講兩句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd14e32beccfb3d716c0fbbe88c975b9d0fc816c","tid":683584,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"501a8c72d9027e3aafed9637a539b6179d6ed74c","tid":683